    {
      "line_1based": 18,
      "serial_label": "L18",
      "text": "Vidgoras apparently realizes his danger and told the US ambassador on 18 February that he may have to \"track down in a dictatorial manner.\" He also indicated that he intends to reshuffle his cabinet, dropping some of the members most identified by the public with graft.",
      "char_len": 270,
